Extract estimated states from an ATA model.

Source: R/fable_ata.R
components.ATA.Rd

Extract estimated states from an ATA model.

# S3 method for ATA
components(object, ...)

Arguments

object

An estimated model.

...

Unused.

Value

A [fabletools::dable()] containing estimated states.

Examples

library(fable.ata)
as_tsibble(USAccDeaths) %>%
  model(ata = AutoATA(value ~ trend("A") + season("A"))) %>% components()
